description: Welcome to a true South Boston rarity, a single-family home offering space, privacy, and convenience all in one. Step inside to find freshly refinished hardwood floors and an open living, dining, and kitchen layout that flows seamlessly onto your spacious private deck, perfect for entertaining or relaxing outdoors. Upstairs, the primary suite provides a comfortable retreat, accompanied by a second bedroom and a second full bath. A convenient half bath on the main floor and in-unit laundry make everyday living effortless. Storage is never an issue with both an attic and an unfinished basement at your disposal. Set on a quiet private way, this home includes the ultimate city luxury, a parking space. With a combination of indoor comfort, outdoor living, and practical amenities, this property is a standout opportunity to own a single-family home in Southie.
